@startuml
title Reminder Lifecycle State Diagram

[*] --> NotScheduled
NotScheduled --> Scheduled : reminderTime set
Scheduled --> Due : reminder time reached
Due --> Sent : WhatsApp send succeeds
Due --> Failed : WhatsApp send fails
Sent --> Rescheduled : reminderTime edited again
Failed --> Scheduled : retry on later tick
Rescheduled --> Due : new reminder time reached

@enduml
